title: Roasted Winter Vegetables
ingredients: ['1 small butternut squash, cubed', '2 red peppers, seeded and diced', '1 sweet potato, peeled and cubed', '3 maris piper potatoes, cubed', '1 red onion, quartered', '1 tablespoon chopped fresh thyme', '2 tablespoons chopped fresh rosemary', '4 tablespoons olive oil', '2 tablespoons balsamic vinegar', 'salt and freshly ground black pepper']
